              comments  to  assist us with keeping our products on the
              leading edge of technology.  We feel no comment  is  too
              small  or too bizarre to warrant investigation.  Keeping
              us informed helps to make your translations  easier  and
              more  cost  effective.  We  work very aggressively to be
              professionals helping professionals. Our greatest joy is
              to see the excitement on the faces of our many users.

              Smile, and welcome to our family of satisfied users.

              From the Developers, Staff, Distributors, and Dealers of
              the LinguaTech line of professional products.

